law.history: Repealed 2012 Ky. Acts ch. 110, sec. 28, effective April 11, 2012. -- Amended 2001 Ky. Acts ch. 58, sec. 3, effective June 21, 2001. -- Created 1996 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 1, sec. 45, effective December 12, 1996.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Governor to include certain appropriations within budget recommendations for benefit reserve fund within Kentucky Workers' Compensation Funding Commission.
